Name:                GtkTV
Version:             0.0.0
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.2
Synopsis:            
Category:            Gtk-based GUIs for Tangible Values
Description:
  GtkTV is a very small library that extends the TV (tangible value)
  framework with graphical user interfaces, using gtk2hs.
  .
